::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike resumes working on the gun, Reptilica looking at Inzola. "You 
can help us replicate this weapons," Reptilica says, going on to explain how 
it functions.

He then looks at Stranato, "Can you bring that over here?" he asks, pointing 
to a large table. The wheels on it were welded, so that the table would not 
slide around during attacks, and it had alot of equipment on top.
